{"tid":1835333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耿爽：關心台胞健康　參與世衛活動須按一中原則","createTime":"2020-01-22T22:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T12:49:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":368,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"65bf3a4df9f194bc3f557ebd930bbeba19d81694","tid":1835333,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:31:56.000Z","msg":"台灣日前確診首宗新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎個案。在北京，外交部發言人耿爽表示，沒有人比大陸政府更關心台灣同胞的健康，強調台灣參加國際組織活動，必須在一個中國原則下，經過兩岸協商，作出合情合理的安排。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說，根據中方與世衛組織的共識，台灣醫療專家可以參加世衛相關技術會議，有需要時，世衛專家可以到台灣考察等。他又說，國家衛健委已及時主動向台灣通報疫情信息，台灣的專家亦已到武漢進行實地考察，對疫情防控、定位處置、醫療整治、病原檢測等問題，進行全面調查，並與大部分參與疫情防控和治療的專家交流。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1504206_1_L_20200122164520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1504206_1_L_20200122164520.jpg&h=6c6b0c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504206-20200122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504206-20200122.htm&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=458b917e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504206-20200122.htm&h=02b1b8d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504206-20200122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e21a094dbb1313fca4e5a392b9b723d0fd9d7e56","tid":1835333,"uid":268106,"like":420,"dislike":1,"score":419,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:35:54.000Z","msg":"死到臨頭仲政治行先<br />\n真係冇得救"},{"pid":"efbb5aef9a13f175c20df02d31eba9d0c072a71a","tid":1835333,"uid":43062,"like":100,"dislike":2,"score":98,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:43:03.000Z","msg":"煩唔煩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 命黎架耿爽"},{"pid":"ec0ac481a9fccfe7297f819a99fb21ec651d0cf8","tid":1835333,"uid":94516,"like":30,"dislike":1,"scor